## 🎥 Recording Setup

### Recommended Tools
- **OBS Studio** (Free) - Professional screen recording
- **Bandicam** (Paid) - User-friendly with excellent quality
- **Windows Game Bar** (Built-in) - Quick and easy option

### Settings
- **Resolution:** 1080x1920 (9:16 aspect ratio)
- **Frame Rate:** 60 FPS for smooth animations
- **Format:** MP4 for universal compatibility
- **Duration:** 60-90 seconds per recording

## 🛠️ Technical Details

### Browser Compatibility
- ✅ Chrome (Recommended)
- ✅ Firefox
- ✅ Safari
- ✅ Edge

### Performance
- **Optimized for 60 FPS** smooth animations
- **Responsive design** adapts to any screen size
- **Memory efficient** particle systems
- **Smooth camera effects** without performance drops

### File Structure
```
📁 Skronicles Animation Studio/
├── 📄 index.html          # Main HTML structure
├── 🎨 styles.css          # All styling and visual design
├── ⚙️ config.js           # Settings and configuration
├── 🎬 animations.js       # Animation functions and effects
├── 🎛️ controls.js         # UI controls and event handlers
├── 🚀 app.js             # Main application initialization
└── 📚 README.md          # This documentation
```

## 🎨 Customization

### Adding New Presets
```javascript
// In config.js, add to presets object:
newpreset: { 
    mood: 'custom', 
    animationStyle: 'particles', 
    speed: 1.0, 
    particleCount: 200 
}
```

### Creating New Moods
```javascript
// In config.js, add to moodColors object:
custom: { 
    bg: ['#color1', '#color2', '#color3'], 
    particles: [hue1, hue2, hue3] 
}
```

### Adding Animation Styles
1. Create new draw function in `animations.js`
2. Add case to switch statement in `animate()`
3. Add option to HTML select element

